-- Standard Chartered Ghana to Pay Preference Dividend
-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 2012-02-21T09:28:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-20/standard-chartered-ghana-to-pay-preference-dividend-on-march-30.html
(Corrects country in second paragraph of story published
yesterday.)  Standard Chartered Bank Ghana Ltd.
will pay a preference-share dividend of 3.24 pesewas per share
for the six months through March 29.  The date of payment is March 30, the Ghanaian lender, a
unit of Standard Chartered Plc said in a statement e-mailed by
the Ghana Stock Exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Moses Mozart Dzawu in Accra at 
 mdzawu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Hilton Shone at 
 hshone@bloomberg.net  